{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2956/comments/77931431.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/JenniferBuehler/gazebo:f1c5c135fb21..f4e51e8f6400?path=gazebo%2Fphysics%2Fode%2FODEHeightmapShape.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2956/_/diff#comment-77931431"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2956, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2956.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2956"}}, "title": "Dart heightmap with bullet and ODE"}, "content": {"raw": "In a similar vein as my earlier [comment](#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2956/dart-heightmap-with-bullet-and-ode/diff#comment-77928118), I think this could be simplified by just using function overloading. So you\u2019d have \n\n```c++\nvoid setOdeHeightfieldDetails(\n    const dHeightfieldDataID odeHeightfieldId,\n    const float* heights,\n    const std::size_t& width,\n    const std::size_t& height,\n    const std::size_t vertSize,\n    double zOffset,\n    double thickness)\n{\n...\n}\n    \nvoid setOdeHeightfieldDetails(\n    const dHeightfieldDataID odeHeightfieldId,\n    const double* heights,\n    const std::size_t& width,\n    const std::size_t& height,\n    const std::size_t vertSize,\n    double zOffset,\n    double thickness)\n{\n...\n}\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In a similar vein as my earlier <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2956/dart-heightmap-with-bullet-and-ode/diff#comment-77928118\" rel=\"nofollow\">comment</a>, I think this could be simplified by just using function overloading. So you\u2019d have </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"nf\">setOdeHeightfieldDetails</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">dHeightfieldDataID</span> <span class=\"n\">odeHeightfieldId</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">float</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">heights</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"n\">width</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"n\">height</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">vertSize</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"kt\">double</span> <span class=\"n\">zOffset</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"kt\">double</span> <span class=\"n\">thickness</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"p\">...</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"nf\">setOdeHeightfieldDetails</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">dHeightfieldDataID</span> <span class=\"n\">odeHeightfieldId</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">double</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">heights</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"n\">width</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"n\">height</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">vertSize</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"kt\">double</span> <span class=\"n\">zOffset</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"kt\">double</span> <span class=\"n\">thickness</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"p\">...</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-10-03T17:06:53.203178+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Addisu Z. Taddese", "uuid": "{9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:90bc87b0-2886-4377-a17c-3a6629a697ff/afbf9be5-1e4c-4810-89d4-e58831f34b11/128"}}, "nickname": "azeey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:90bc87b0-2886-4377-a17c-3a6629a697ff"}, "inline": {"to": 103, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/physics/ode/ODEHeightmapShape.cc"}, "updated_on": "2018-10-03T17:06:53.214797+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 77931431}